Chapter 1: Olive cultivation: characteristics and varieties (16 hours)
Specific objectives: at the end of this chapter, the trainee will be able to:
1. discover the specifications of the olive tree (morphology);
2. link between Olive planting places and climatic requirements and soil type;
3. distinguish local olive varieties from their foreign varieties; and
4. plant the olive tree.
