1. introduction of the olive tree (anatomic parts and functions);
2. climatic requirements of olive growing: temperature-moisture-light;
3. determination of soil quality suitable for olive cultivation (identification of the importance of soil
examination);
4. identification of Lebanese and international varieties; and
5. cultivation of olive trees

