How determine the optimal harvesting time
The optimal harvesting time could be determined monitoring:
 The trend of fruits drops, the fresh and dry weight of fruits, the oil accumulation, the
pigmentation, the fruit attachment force and the hardness of the drupes;
 the amount of oil yields from plants;
 the change of the acid composition, the phenols content, the substances responsible for the
fruity flavour, etc.
The most important ripening indexes are:
 Colour of fruits;
 Fruit attachment force;
 Fruits drop;
 Fruits hardness;
 Oil content.

